  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to pavucontrol-qt</title>

    <para>
      <application>pavucontrol-qt</application> is the Qt port of volume
      control pavucontrol of sound server PulseAudio. Its use is not limited
      to LXQt.
    </para>

    &lfs7a_checked;

